    <objectives>
      <material>
        <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;h1&gt;Session 21 Quiz – AI Strategies&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test your understanding of AI algorithms, strategy patterns, and decision-making code.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Topics Covered:&lt;/strong&gt;
- Random, greedy, and conservative AI
- Card comparison and sorting
- Strategy pattern implementation
- Predictive AI and game analysis
- Difficulty levels&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions:&lt;/strong&gt;
- 16 questions from the Session 21 question bank
- 20 minute time limit
- 3 attempts allowed
- 16 points total (1 point per question)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;After syncing the question bank to Canvas:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</mattext>
      </material>
    </objectives>
